nodes.text: Wom-Nii Gnaden was a male Jedi Master active in the last decades of the Galactic Republic. He took part in the Battle of Crombach Nebula, during the Clone Wars, where his NTB-630 naval bomber crashed into a Munificent-class star frigate. By the time of the Battle of Coruscant in 19 BBY, the impact mark of the collision was still visible on the frigate.
